{"tid":1146094,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"90後新谷招人啊！","createTime":"2019-05-09T04:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T10:58:52.000Z","uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"255dfe9b76b9e48e405f42bc3912c6d5d6703888","tid":1146094,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:49:17.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家入黎傾下計熱鬧下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比個谷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n預計周不時都會搞好多聚會<br />\n例如 打機 飯聚 唱K 行街shopping 飲野 bbq 踩單車 乜活動都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地大部份人都好得閒<br />\n入黎肯出聲就一定會覆你陪你9up 吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有感情問題我地都有經驗豐富嘅谷友開解你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對新人仲會好好添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宗旨都係想大家出到社會識唔到朋友<br />\n可以比大家一個谷識到可能做到一世嘅好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚴禁5p仔厹入黎搵sp食女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加嚴禁娘娘入黎玩感情收兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一經發現或收到舉報唔會通知即踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外為咗唔想絲打出到黎聚驚冇女仔陪<br />\n巴打又唔想一齊格劍嘅話<br />\n我地男女比例會平衡返小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未入到嘅請耐心等候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfiXcpIKDmRDMVGx1VNgVBMsBW1EliETnUMcDFRe-tB_AJ4Yw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfiXcpIKDmRDMVGx1VNgVBMsBW1EliETnUMcDFRe-tB_AJ4Yw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYV3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=1472631c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfiXcpIKDmRDMVGx1VNgVBMsBW1EliETnUMcDFRe-tB_AJ4Yw/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n想加入嘅巴絲打請填一填先<br />\n我地有專人on call check名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後由於假人太多<br />\n冇icon嘅會低啲機會入到㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望下一個朋友係認識到你"},{"pid":"b3c4fc587ccbfa8945cb9deb30ea70be852d453f","tid":1146094,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90109475b2088401686c957108a2b426867dc78b","tid":1146094,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dec8e55ecb7eed9872b7ee6bcfd3fb05931d052","tid":1146094,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T05:23:29.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"ff694745f9585b12617cace1327d080e43dfa704","tid":1146094,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T06:00:33.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"b4888eb35db5521cac88e165639e94867601f8bc","tid":1146094,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"32b53673dbfc893a8aa2bc6b825f132475cbb4b7","tid":1146094,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"c02c735414823b333d9e1971b413b61508ae306a","tid":1146094,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"f6ad0f3c004a99d04719b8fb47edf50deb02aece","tid":1146094,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"8615365f6c1a55719f9554b996d82373132cb38a","tid":1146094,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"41a8257a6037a94e91e8c2cbb